    <title type="html"><![CDATA[Never trust the justice system]]></title>
    <link href="http://gnuconsulting.com//blog/2011/01/24/never-trust-the-justice-system/"/>
    <updated>2011-01-24T12:15:50-05:00</updated>
    <id>http://gnuconsulting.com//blog/2011/01/24/never-trust-the-justice-system</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><a href="http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2006/06/24/AR2006062401082_pf.html">Repeat after me: never trust that the justice system works.</a>  <a href="http://boingboing.net/2008/07/28/law-prof-and-cop-agr.html">Never talk to a cop</a>.  Never sign anything presented to you by a cop unless your lawyer has told you to. Never, ever, think that things will work themselves out because you&rsquo;re a good person and surely this is all just a big mistake.</p>
]]></content>
